    "title": "Organ Priority Data for Chemical Risk & Cumulation Scoring",
    "description": "Compiled from ATSDR, EPA, SOFA score (ICU n=63756), STP toxicology, GHS/STOT, AstraZeneca FTiM studies (n=77 drugs), NCI-CTCAE v5, and PMC toxicology literature.",
    "sources": [
      "ATSDR CSEM - Organ Systems Affected by Toxic Exposure (CDC, 2015)",
      "EPA Guidelines for Health Risk Assessment of Chemical Mixtures (1986, updated 2024)",
      "SOFA Score mortality data - PMC9322581 (63,756 ICU patients)",
      "Society of Toxicologic Pathology (STP) - Organ Weight Recommendations (2007)",
      "AstraZeneca FTiM target organ study - PubMed 23422911 (77 candidate drugs)",
      "NCI Common Terminology Criteria for Adverse Events (CTCAE) v5.0",
      "GHS Specific Target Organ Toxicity (STOT-SE / STOT-RE) classification",
      "PMC6172960 - ToxRefDB 20 target organ ML study",
      "PMC9205464 - In silico organ toxicity (heart, kidney, lung)"
    ],
    "last_updated": "2026-04-24"
  },

